
Practical 12: NotebookLM Project

Aim

To create revision notes using NotebookLM.

Objectives
	•	To generate study guide
	•	To create flashcards

Materials Required
	•	NotebookLM

Procedure
	
1. Create NotebookLM project – Start a new project in NotebookLM to organize your materials and AI-generated outputs in one workspace.


2. Upload two resources – Add two documents or sources to the project so the AI can analyze and reference them.


3. Generate study guide – Use NotebookLM’s tools to create a structured study guide summarizing key concepts from the uploaded resources.


4. Generate flashcards – Automatically produce flashcards that highlight important facts, terms, or ideas for easier review.


5. Review accuracy – Carefully check the summaries and flashcards to ensure all information is correct and reflects the original resources.


6. Take screenshots – Capture screenshots of the study guide and flashcards to document your work or include them in your submission.





